[31m-## English[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 1. Login and Basics[m
[31m-- Start the app, choose a language, and log in.[m
[31m-- You can switch between light/dark theme.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 2. Daily Report[m
[31m-- Select Date/Shift/Area and save the basic info.[m
[31m-- Fill in Key Output / Issues / Countermeasures and save.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 3. Attendance[m
[31m-- Enter Regular / Contract attendance data and save.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 4. Equipment / Lot[m
[31m-- Create and edit equipment logs and lot logs.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 5. Delay List[m
[31m-- Search by date range (Start/End).[m
[31m-- Import Excel/CSV/TXT, then upload after review.[m
[31m-- Double-click a cell to edit directly (Date supports manual input).[m
[31m-- Right-click to delete selected rows.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 6. Summary Actual[m
[31m-- Search by date range (Start/End).[m
[31m-- Import Excel/CSV/TXT, then upload after review.[m
[31m-- Right-click to delete selected rows.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### 7. Calendar[m
[31m-- Date fields are editable.[m
[31m-- Use the ?Today? button in the calendar popup.[m
